<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idf004b61a-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s7318"><num value="7318">§ 7318.</num><heading> Termination of Commission</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Commission shall terminate on submission of the final report required by <ref href="/us/usc/t7/s7314">section 7314 of this title</ref>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idf004b61b-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/pl/104/127/tI/s188">Pub. L. 104–127, title I, § 188</ref>, <date date="1996-04-04">Apr. 4, 1996</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/110/941">110 Stat. 941</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
